N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 3 ยง 203.15 - John william campo

State Regulations

The Banking Board hereby grants permission for John William

Campo to be at the same time a director of Central State Bank and a registered
representative of Ter Bush & Putnam Securities, Inc., a company engaged in
the retail sale of shares of various open-end mutual funds. Notes
